    * NEWS: Added pg_fetch_assoc()

    * ext/pgsql/pgsql.c: Use PGSQL_CONV_FORCE_NULL as it is supposed.
    PGSQL_CONV_FORCE_NULL inserts NULL to field instead of
    NULL string for string type tuples.

