      sapi/cgi/config.m4
      sapi/cli/config.m4:
    Made PHP_ADD_LIBPATH use the $ld_runpath_switch and changed the Darwin
    link lines in sapi/cli and sapi/cgi to use $NATIVE_RPATHS.
    This is a tentative fix for #18450.

